  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Gielas Hotel guests have an extensive hot and cold buffet breakfast <span>served in Restaurant Kaltio, located on the ground floor of the Gielas building.</span></p>
<p>All evening meals are served in the Tunturi Hotel's main building (approx. 100 metre walk). This is a three course buffet dinner with a choice of main courses, including a vegetarian option, two desserts, soup and a salad buffet.</p>
<p>New Years gala dinner and dance included.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
