  <description><![CDATA[<p>The luxury Gielas Hotel offers highly recommended deluxe rooms and junior suites, located in the deluxe wing of the <a data-udi="umb://document/3f5398805f5841a28e1f5829945f8748" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f5398805f5841a28e1f5829945f8748}" title="Tunturi Hotel">Tunturi Hotel</a>. This unique hotel offers you a chance to experience the beauty of the Arctic wilderness while enjoying comfortable amenities. The Gielas Hotel offers it's own fireside lounge, bar and a la carte restaurant - the perfect spot to relax after a day of exploring <a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka">Saariselkä</a><em>.</em></p>
<h2>Village location</h2>
<p><span></span><span>The Gielas Hotel has an excellent location in <a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka">Saariselkä</a>, set back around 250 metres from the main village. Its location makes it a great starting point for outdoor activities such as tobogganing, winter walking, cross-country skiing, and participating in optional extra excursions such as Northern Light experiences and snowmobile safaris.</span></p>
<h2><span>Luxury accommodation</span></h2>
<p>The hotel offers superior rooms furnished in a simplistic style that have been designed to provide a cosy retreat after a day out in the snow. <span>The rooms are equipped with everything you need for a Lapland holiday, including a balcony overlooking the resort, free Wi-Fi, drying closest, tea and coffee making facilities and a sauna.</span></p>
<h2><span>Lounge and bar</span></h2>
<p>After a day of skiing or participating in one of our excursions, the lounge and bar area is an ideal spot to curl up next to the fire with a hot chocolate. Alternatively, enjoy a drink in the Bar &amp; Grill Pirtti, which has a laid-back home away from home feel, or sit back and relax with the live entertainment, which is frequently on during the winter season.</p>
<p><span>Gielas Hotel guests have breakfast in their own hotel and take dinner in the main building of the Tunturi Hotel.</span></p>
<p> </p>
<p><em><span>This hotel can also be booked as part of our '<a data-udi="umb://document/fa265f887e1d4825bb39ee25d66f2714" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fa265f887e1d4825bb39ee25d66f2714}" title="Muotka 2-Centre Adventure">Muotka 2-Centre Adventure</a>'. </span></em></p>]]></description>
